Claro! Segue um .gitignore abrangente para um projeto Spring Boot (Maven), cobrindo IDEs comuns, arquivos temporários, logs, relatórios de testes, configurações locais e artefatos de build. Mantive os arquivos do Maven Wrapper permitidos (devem ser commitados).

```.gitignore (gitignore)
# ==========================================
# SISTEMA OPERACIONAL
# ==========================================
# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Linux
*~

# ==========================================
# IDEs E EDITORES
# ==========================================

# Ignorar bytecode Java
*.class

# Ignorar artefatos empacotados
*.jar

# IntelliJ IDEA
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
# Arquivos de projeto JetBrains (já existentes)
# Default ignored files
/shelf/
/workspace.xml
# Editor-based HTTP Client requests
/httpRequests/
# Datasource local storage ignored files
/dataSources/
/dataSources.local.xml

# Eclipse
.project
.classpath
.settings/
.factorypath

# VS Code
.vscode/

# NetBeans
/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/dist/
/.nb-gradle/

# ==========================================
# BUILD / SAÍDA
# ==========================================
target/
build/
out/
bin/
dependency-reduced-pom.xml

# ==========================================
# LOGS E DUMPS
# ==========================================
logs/
*.log
*.log.*
hs_err_pid*
replay_pid*
heapdump.hprof
*.hprof

# ==========================================
# SPRING / CONFIG LOCAL
# (Mantenha exemplos versionados ex.: application-example.yml)
# ==========================================
application-local.properties
application-local.yml
application-*.local.properties
application-*.local.yml
application-*.secret.properties
application-*.secret.yml
secrets.*
*.secrets.*
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Keystores/Certs locais (não versionar chaves reais)
*.jks
*.p12
*.pfx
*.pem
*.crt
*.key

# ==========================================
# TESTES/RELATÓRIOS
# ==========================================
surefire-reports/
failsafe-reports/
jacoco.exec
.jacoco/
.site/

# ==========================================
# DOCKER/CONTAINERS
# ==========================================
docker/*.env
docker/.env
compose.override.yml
docker-compose.override.yml

# ==========================================
# MISC
# ==========================================
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig
*.rej

# ==========================================
# MAVEN WRAPPER
# (NÃO ignore .mvn/; o wrapper deve ser commitado)
# ==========================================
!.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
```